{"tid":499932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 差婆 風化島 龍友 ] 人中之龍極2 討論區 4","createTime":"2017-12-15T10:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T04:01:59.000Z","uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbb1d9c8e32eb4f73d2da3a79abdb2fb114c2e0","tid":499932,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1cBxq1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1cBxq1v.jpg&h=cda0c423&s={SIZE}\" />[/center]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方近期宣佈 人中之龍 極2 體驗版將於日服PSN <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">11月22日</span></strong>推出，雖然暫時只公佈日本地區 (日服PSN)，但根據上次人中之龍6 既經驗，好有機會同上次一樣同步開放，當然要再等官方宣佈為準。<br />\n(體驗版既Save會繼承)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">人龍極2故事背景:</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事主要圍繞多年前原作「人中之龍2」桐生一馬所屬的東城會，同關西幫會近江連合旗下鄉龍會「關西之龍」鄉田龍司作出全面對決: 關東 vs 關西<br />\n<br />\n《極2》故事的骨幹跟隨原作之外，在本作中會加入真島吾朗的新故事，主題是「真島吾朗的真相」。<br />\n 追加故事劇情將敘述初代作品《人中之龍》與《人中之龍 2》之間所發生的故事。<br />\n<br />\n《人中之龍 2》的真島，因「某事件」而離開東城會。<br />\n在本次追加的故事劇情中，將公開這尚未解開的謎團。此外，在這追加故事劇情中，真島吾朗將變為可操作角色。<br />\n另外真島更會自人龍0以來，首次再度回到蒼天堀"},{"pid":"e1698b8e73f17e88df6bfa359844f3161082e4be","tid":499932,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:36:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">遊戲元素:</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n風化島回歸 (悅子回歸) <br />\n另外官方確認風化島參與既女優包括 明日花綺羅、AIKA、高橋聖子、桃乃木香奈、三上悠亞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fwEXGZs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfwEXGZs.jpg&h=fae7ec08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NJ7rGAt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNJ7rGAt.jpg&h=cc9d1a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統、以及「極」睇宣傳片所見終於變返好似以前咁<br />\n我一直認為人龍6換系統之餘仲搵左咁多大牌影星配音超支先令戰鬥系統變垃圾，今集似乎改善晒依d問題"},{"pid":"d31c058a487c1de7ba475a57801355728f490064","tid":499932,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">人中之龍 極2 前背景重溫</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然人中之龍0 &rarr; 極 &rarr; 極2  咁順住玩落去既話會好好多。但未玩過前作既話都值得入手，故事都只係成個系列既其中一章<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人龍0 以及人龍極 除左真島既轉變令人深刻之外，桐生失去錦山、由美 兩位一齊長大既「家人」既悲慘經歷都令人好深刻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJBqg5bavbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJJBqg5bavbk&d=49Z45uPvrCJedagPJ%2FldkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=29ee8c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJBqg5bavbk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然錦山既黑化可以理解，但我由此至終都相信錦山確實曾經當過桐生係兄弟， <br />\n桐生十年冤獄 錦山雖然無去探過一次監 我諗只係錦山內心既唔肯面對自己既懦弱，就同佢有勇氣殺堂島宗兵但無勇氣承擔一樣。<br />\n但可惜最終錦山敵不過妒忌心， 以德報怨"},{"pid":"e698f13751b38fde8d0751a0d24d6cd7765c0d0f","tid":499932,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/222238_ac63b1ea7c99222d14f6917a66d5d6eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F222238_ac63b1ea7c99222d14f6917a66d5d6eb.jpg&h=ceaec5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/222240_1ab6cd36cdb9d985066cb64c337721a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F222240_1ab6cd36cdb9d985066cb64c337721a1.jpg&h=602c47f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒼天崛J4 要做支線任務 復仇代理人 完成獎勵"},{"pid":"4be835175fe9a56befd510574d045f00a4b7a113","tid":499932,"uid":6078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"905ff495e60fef0b5135aeb36e016bd1754b9478","tid":499932,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"sore ga ware wa goro majima<br />\nmajima~ ken~se~tsu~~"},{"pid":"e01176423120554141c84e9dae1d6c165c00af65","tid":499932,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"日本雷鬼龐克樂團 SiM 擔當新曲「A」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hdf7gIW_hls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhdf7gIW_hls&d=49Z45uPvrCJedagPJ%2FldkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=013e4262\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hdf7gIW_hls</a>"},{"pid":"b2039fcddcae8eecd9c8acd4127c3ea5f719af99","tid":499932,"uid":35895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:09:23.000Z","msg":"留定名先"},{"pid":"7317d3543baad3db0e208a43a43052a4de6df085","tid":499932,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"sorry 閞錯吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[ 差婆 風化島 龍友 ] 人中之龍極2 討論區 5<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/499974/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/499974/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"89fa5cf955cf8a6e97ff9b9b75eabdd8275bac1f","tid":499932,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:25:45.000Z","msg":"解到個麻將任了 唔該本命巴打<br />\n原來咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d0ff2c20af9632f40e552f3c02cb94722a97ae","tid":499932,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T21:21:25.000Z","msg":"依家玩到第3章，想問下幾時先會返神室町？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be70320b7a0e7ee6127921c2f1f008a9cf08f976","tid":499932,"uid":109809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"lm先"},{"pid":"13f4978bac13b9dfaedfc4d46617500e143b8885","tid":499932,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"有幾多章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"